{"title":"Rapha launches new range of ‘Performance Trailwear’ for mountain bikers","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/rapha-performance-trailwear/","date":1622728844000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-launches-their-new-range-14-b8af81b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620,413\" />                                            <p>“After 17 years of innovating road and gravel apparel, now is the right time for Rapha to enter the mountain bike market”, says Rapha’s MTB general manager, Jake Rosenbloum.</p>\n<p>The new Performance Trailwear range that launches today includes both men’s and women’s lines and comprises pretty much everything you’d need to <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/what-to-wear-mountain-biking/\">wear out on the trails</a>.</p>\n<p>All of the new Trailwear incorporate “environmentally-preferred” materials – as it stands, these make up 43 per cent of the fabrics currently used, but Rapha has committed to using 90 per cent environmentally-preferred materials by 2025 across the range.</p>\n<p>Rapha says that these fabrics are technical, tough and have been tested in the roughest natural environments.</p>\n<section><div>\n        <h2>Five things you need to know about the new Rapha Performance Trailwear</h2>\n<ol><li>The new Rapha MTB range has a separate women’s and men’s line of clothing</li>\n<li>Along with clothing, Rapha is also offering a number of MTB-focused accessories, including a hip-pack and co-branded Smith Forefront 2 helmet</li>\n<li>Made using “environmentally-preferred materials”</li>\n<li>Most garments will include a repair patch kit for quick and easy fixes. For bigger repair jobs, clothing can be sent back to Rapha to be fixed for free</li>\n<li>Rapha to launch a series of initiatives to support trail organisations across the UK and US</li>\n</ol><p>\n\n    </p></div>\n    </section><div>\n    <img /></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Pro riders provided technical feedback on the performance of the kit during product development.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Rapha</i></span></div>\n<p>Rapha has been smart with the riders it’s chosen to help develop and test this latest line of kit. Riders such as Jill Kintner, Ella Conolly and Bryn Atkinson know what it takes to perform at the highest level and, between them, have years of experience when it comes to providing technical feedback for product development.</p>\n<p>What’s a real bonus for many mountain bikers is that Rapha will supply a repair kit with most products, which should help to deal with quick fixes if you snag a jersey or get a small rip in your shorts.</p>\n<p>But, thankfully, if your nice new kit is in need of a bigger repair, Rapha says that you can send the product back for it to be repaired free of charge, when possible.</p>\n<div>\n    <img /></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Most products come with a repair kit.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Rapha</i></span></div>\n<h2>Women’s Rapha Performance Trailwear range</h2>\n<p>Here’s what’s included in the women’s Rapha Performance Trailwear collection.</p>\n<h3>Women’s Trail Technical T-shirt</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-launches-their-new-range-04-e59593c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha’s Women’s Trail Technical T-shirt is light and breathable and designed to be durable and snag-resistant.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Technical-T-shirt-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-1-5e4eacc.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Technical T-shirt in Grey.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Technical-T-shirt-Amaranth-Micro-Chip-1-f9796d5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Technical T-shirt in Amaranth.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£55 / $75 / €65</li>\n</ul><p>This light and breathable tech tee should be durable and snag-resistant, and do a good job at wicking sweat from your body.</p>\n<p>It’s made from low-impact recycled materials and comes with a patch kit to repair it should you need to.</p>\n<h3>Women’s Trail Tank</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-launches-their-new-range-01-03180fd.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The Women’s Trail Tank is ideal for warmer days out.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Tank-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-1-1b19e01.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Tank in Grey.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Tank-Amaranth-Micro-Chip-1-ec67543.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Tank in Amaranth.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£50 / $70 / €60</li>\n</ul><p>If you like to ride in hotter climates (so probably not the UK, then), this might well be for you.</p>\n<p>Like the tech tee, the Trail Tank is designed to be light and breathable, and is made from recycled materials.</p>\n<h3>Women’s Trail Lightweight Jacket</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Lightweight-Jacket-Micro-Chip-Anthracite-2-7bf10d1.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail lightweight jacket in White.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Lightweight-Jacket-Amaranth-Micro-Chip-2-aadaea5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail lightweight jacket in Amaranth.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£130 / $180 / €155</li>\n</ul><p>The Trail jacket is constructed from a windproof, ripstop nylon fabric that’s claimed to be light, breathable and tear-resistant.</p>\n<p>It comes with a storage strap that, once the jacket is packed up inside its very own chest pocket, will let you attach it to the bike. The under-helmet-hood is adjustable.</p>\n<p>While this isn’t going to keep you dry and warm in a heavy downpour, it should be easy to carry and will keep the chill out on a blustery day.</p>\n<h3>Women’s Trail ¾ Sleeve Jersey</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-3-4-Jersey-Micro-chip-Anthracite-1-03ddf4d.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail ¾ sleeve jersey in White.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-3-4-Jersey-Amaranth-Anthracite-1-a3839a8.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail ¾ sleeve jersey in Amaranth.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£75 / $100 / €90</li>\n</ul><p>This jersey is snag-resistant, made from 100 per cent recycled materials and is designed to be light and breathable.</p>\n<h3>Women’s Trail Shorts</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Shorts-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-2-3b81224.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Shorts in Black.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Shorts-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-3-3b81224.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha’s Women’s Trail Shorts have two zipped pockets.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Shorts-Amaranth-Micro-Chip-2-6c24725.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Shorts in Amaranth.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Shorts-Amaranth-Micro-Chip-3-6c24725.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Shorts should work with knee pads.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£110 / $150 / €135</li>\n</ul><p>These are made from a plain weave stretch nylon and feature a low-profile stretch waist to try to help boost on-the-bike comfort.</p>\n<p>There are two zipped pockets, one of which features a phone sleeve and Rapha says that the cut will work just fine with or without knee pads.</p>\n<h3>Women’s Trail Short Liner</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Liner-Basic-Black-1-a8b8694.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Women’s Trail Liner in Basic Black.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Liner-Basic-Black-2-82482db.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>There are mesh panels on either side to help prevent overheating.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Womens-Trail-Liner-Basic-Black-3-ed32da0.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The liner includes Rapha’s chamois pad.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£80 / $110 / €95</li>\n</ul><p>Using its years of experience in making road kit, Rapha has tried to apply this to the new Women’s Trail short liner.</p>\n<p>Mesh panels at either side are there to help prevent overheating, while the chamois pad should hopefully keep you comfy while pedalling.</p>\n<h2>Men’s Rapha Performance Trailwear range</h2>\n<p>The men’s range doesn’t offer quite as many products as the women’s, and while Rapha offers equivalents in both lines, there are some differences.</p>\n<h3>Trail Technical T-shirt</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Technical-T-shirt-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-1-e83969f.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Technical T-shirt in Grey.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Technical-T-shirt-Mayfly-Anthracite-1-1a591e3.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Technical T-shirt in Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Technical-T-shirt-Micro-Chip-Anthracite-1-1a591e3.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Technical T-shirt in White.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Technical-T-shirt-Pageant-Blue-Scarlet-Ibis-1-1a591e3.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Technical T-shirt in Pageant Blue.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£55 / $75 / €65</li>\n</ul><p>Just like the women’s version, this tech tee is designed to be light and breathable, and should wick sweat away from the skin.</p>\n<h3>Trail Lightweight Jacket</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Lightweight-Jacket-Micro-Chip-Anthracite-2-72b26d3.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail lightweight Jacket in White.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Lightweight-Jacket-Pageant-Blue-Scarlet-Ibis-2-0556a3e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail lightweight Jacket in Pageant Blue.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Lightweight-Jacket-Anthracite-Micro-chip-2-6998340.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail lightweight Jacket in Black.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£130 / $180 / €155</li>\n</ul><p>Rapha says that the cut of this easy-to-pack jacket should work on and off the bike.</p>\n<p>While it’s windproof, it has been given a DWR (durable water repellency) treatment so should help to fend off lighter rain showers too.</p>\n<h3>Trail ¾ Sleeve Jersey</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-3-4-Jersey-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-1-5f15c0a.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail ¾ Sleeve Jersey in Grey.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-3-4-Jersey-Pageant-Blue-Scarlet-Ibis-1-9624d24.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail ¾ Sleeve Jersey in Pageant Blue.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-3-4-Jersey-Micro-Chip-Anthracite-1-2143fb7.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail ¾ Sleeve Jersey in White.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-3-4-Jersey-Mayfly-Anthracite-1-0c712ec.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail ¾ Sleeve Jersey in Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£75 / $100 / €90</li>\n</ul><p>The cut may be very slightly different, but the features here are otherwise the same as on the women’s version.</p>\n<p>Rapha says its strong, durable woven fabric should help to protect the jersey from branches and brambles, as well as the odd tumble.</p>\n<h3>Trail Shorts</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Shorts-Pageant-Blue-Scarlet-Ibis-2-17ed6a5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Shorts in Pageant Blue.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Shorts-Pageant-Blue-Scarlet-Ibis-3-17ed6a5.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The men’s shorts get two hip pockets, plus two zipped pockets lower down the legs.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Shorts-Mayfly-Anthracite-2-aafd368.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Shorts in Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Shorts-Mayfly-Anthracite-3-aafd368.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>There are two adjusters at the waist to tailor fit.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Shorts-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-2-468889d.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Shorts in Black.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Shorts-Anthracite-Micro-Chip-3-aafd368.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha has included belt loops too.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£110 / $150 / €135</li>\n</ul><p>The men’s shorts get two hip pockets, plus two zipped pockets lower down the legs to stash essentials, and an integrated phone sleeve.</p>\n<p>While there are two adjusters at the waist to tailor fit, Rapha has included belt loops too, which seems an odd move on a trail short. The cut should work with or without knee pads.</p>\n<h3>Trail Cargo Bib Liner</h3>\n<div>\n    <img /></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Rapha’s Cargo Bib Liner in Basic Black.</span></figcaption><span></span></div>\n<ul><li>£100 / $135 / €120</li>\n</ul><p>These bib liners feature two pockets at the rear to help carry essentials and avoid having to wear a pack.</p>\n<p>Mesh side panels help to keep them cooler and a padded chamois should keep your undercarriage comfy on long rides. These are made from recycled material too.</p>\n<h2>Rapha Performance Trailwear accessories</h2>\n<p>Alongside the trail wear staples, Rapha is offering a number of additional items. These include…</p>\n<h3>Trail Hip Pack</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Hip-Pack-Anthracite-_-Micro-Chip_1-810a436.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha’s Trail Hip Pack in Black.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Hip-Pack-Anthracite-_-Micro-Chip_2-f873894.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The Trail Hip Pack fits two bottles and has space to secure kit on the top too via the external drawcord.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Hip-Pack-Mayfly-_-Anthracite_2-0344f00-1.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Hip Pack in Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Trail-Hip-Pack-Pageant-Blue-_-Scarlet-Ibis_1-d784797-1.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha Trail Hip Pack in Pageant Blue.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£60 / $80 / €70</li>\n</ul><p>This form-fitting, highly adjustable little pack can stow two water bottles and has a total 3-litre capacity for all your other bits and pieces.</p>\n<p>Inside the front pocket you’ll find a key clip, while outside there’s an external drawcord that can be used to tether bulkier items down.</p>\n<h3>Rapha x Smith Forefront 2 Helmet</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-x-Smith-Forefront-2-Trail-Helmet-Asphalt-_-Micro-Chip-_-Anthracite_1-fdee3be.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The Rapha x Smith Forefront 2 helmet is available in a choice of colours, including this Anthracite option.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-x-Smith-Forefront-2-Trail-Helmet-Asphalt-_-Micro-Chip-_-Anthracite_5-3ee5607-1.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The Rapha x Smith Forefront 2 helmet features Koroyd and MIPS technology.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-x-Smith-Forefront-2-Trail-Helmet-Asphalt-_-Micro-Chip-_-Anthracite_3-fdee3be.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>A front-on look at the Rapha x Smith Forefront 2 helmet.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-x-Smith-Forefront-2-Trail-Helmet-Asphalt-_-Micro-Chip-_-Anthracite_4-fdee3be.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Sunglasses can be stashed on the helmet.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-x-Smith-Forefront-2-Trail-Helmet-Anthracite-_-Mayfly-_-Micro-Chip_1-119e2f9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha x Smith Forefront 2 Trail Helmet in Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Rapha-x-Smith-Forefront-2-Trail-Helmet-Anthracite-_-Mayfly-_-Micro-Chip_3-119e2f9.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Rapha x Smith Forefront 2 Trail Helmet in Black.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£175 / $240 / €205</li>\n</ul><p>The Forefront 2 offers plenty of head coverage and uses Koroyd and MIPS technology in a bid to better protect your head in the event of a crash.</p>\n<p>While the peak will shift up enough to allow you to stash goggles underneath, you can also stow glasses at the rear.</p>\n<h3>Pro Team full-frame glasses</h3>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Pro-Team-Full-Frame-Glasses-f90ad54.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Case for the Pro Team full-frame glasses.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Pro-Team-Full-Frame-Sunglasses-Mayfly-_-Micro-Chip_1-88130c2.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Pro Team full-frame glasses in Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Pro-Team-Full-Frame-Sunglasses-Mayfly-_-Micro-Chip_2-b1b177b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Small logo detail on the arm.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Pro-Team-Full-Frame-Sunglasses-Mayfly-_-Micro-Chip_3-560e32b.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The specs come with a clear lens that can be swapped out.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Pro-Team-Full-Frame-Sunglasses-Micro-Chip-_-Asphalt_1-7284b0c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>Different sized nose pieces are available.<br /></span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure><div>\n    <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/05/Pro-Team-Full-Frame-Sunglasses-Micro-Chip-_-Asphalt_2-49f8921.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" /></div>    <figcaption><div>\n    <figcaption><span>The Pro Team full-frame glasses are available in Grey (here) and Mayfly.</span>\n    </figcaption><span>\n                    <i>Rapha</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption></figure></div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<ul><li>£120 / $165 / €145</li>\n</ul><p>These full-frame specs come with a clear lens that can be swapped out, and different sized nose pieces to tailor to different nose shapes.</p>\n<p><em>We have kit on the way and will be doing full reviews once we’ve had a decent amount of time testing it all.</em></p>","author":"Robin Weaver","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"7d65b1caa8b5f585c4b7dca3483d6cc0a79f0549dfbff1d4b6945856273aa41a","category":"Cycling"}